btop: btop (a terminal based system resource monitor with themes)
btop:
btop: Resource monitor that shows usage and stats for processor, memory, 
btop: disks, network and processes. C++ version and continuation of bashtop 
btop: and bpytop.
btop:
btop: - Easy to use, with a game inspired menu system.
btop: - Full mouse support
btop: - Fast and responsive UI with UP, DOWN key process selection.
btop: - Graph for network usage, IO activity and speeds for disks
btop: - And more...
